A first of it's kind Video Podcast. All videos are filmed and edited using an iPhone.  The podcast features a typical day as an Annual Pass Member at Universal Studios Hollywood in Universal City, California. There are special edition episodes that feature rides &amp; attractions, plus special events. Upcoming interviews with people who have filmed at Universal Studios Hollywood on the backlot are in the works. Park Review episodes average 2-3 minutes and Special Edition Episodes average 2-4 minutes.  Episodes are designed to bring the viewer into the park and allow them to feel like they are there also.  The short videos allow for easy viewing without a long format to watch. Live Tweets and Facebook postings give previews to the Park Review episodes while they are being filmed. The website UniversalAnnualPass.us is a simple website designed like a photo album and links to each podcast episode to make it easy to locate what interested each individual.&#xD;
